    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the S54 3.2L straight-six, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Beisan VANOS overhaul. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates, ensuring chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual shifts with surgical precision, paired with a variable M-differential that remains tight and responsive. Every bushing, mount, and damper is in peak condition, preserving the communicative steering rack and 50/50 weight distribution. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance, consistent paint depth across all panels, and flawless mechanical synchronicities.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. Original factory paint. Smoke-free interior. Full service records included. Clean title in hand.",
